###
@providerId = rustfs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/providers/{{providerId}}/buckets

### browse
@bucketName = data
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/providers/{{providerId}}/buckets/{{bucketName}}/browse?path=iceberg

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/providers/{{providerId}}/buckets/{{bucketName}}/download?
    key={{$random.alphanumeric(8)}}

###
